# Secrets — never commit
.secrets/
**/.env
.env.*
.aws/
*.pem
*.ppk
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
*.key

# Private interview prep — never published (per EXP_REPORT_2026-06-11_Portfolio-Repo-Restart-and-Authenticity)
*.private.md

# Internal Navi project-management docs — local memory only, not recruiter-facing
