docs/reports/
docs/*.md
docs/learning/JOB_MILESTONES.md
docs/learning/JIRA.md
docs/learning/LEARNING_STATE.md
docs/learning/CLAUDE_TEACHING_RULES.md
docs/learning/prompts/
docs/learning/ROADMAP.md
